{"tid":1986660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天文台冀添置高性能電腦系統為市民提供概率天氣服務","createTime":"2020-04-24T03:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T06:57:01.000Z","uid":241764,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4b7614d8b743fcd77d3b7cb72208d6be45eca548","tid":1986660,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"立法會財委會早上審議涉及共1億3800萬元，以更換大帽山的風暴探測天氣雷達，以及購置高性能電腦系統的撥款申請。<br />\n<br />\n天文台助理台長劉心怡表示，目前天文台的天氣預報承諾準確度是88%，希望購入的高性能電腦系統後，能為市民提供概率天氣服務，讓市民為出行做準備。由於高性能電腦換代速度快，天文台是否購買新電腦系統，要視乎天文台的運算能力，以及服務需要等。<br />\n<br />\n大帽山雷達已運作約20年，當局預計2022年後將難以正常運作。天文台說，一般要求雷達供應商在標書承諾提供零部件10至15年，並會在供應商停止生產部件前購入部件以作儲備，以延長雷達服務期限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522463-20200424.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522463-20200424.htm&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=24ca559e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522463-20200424.htm&h=251ebda5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522463-20200424.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b72e51deccd3d0baadb55278d2fcb7c50ff03b","tid":1986660,"uid":151074,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"算吧啦！咪又係9至4無黑雨8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a89069d873d22ad3a9fa838b29df5b201432b1","tid":1986660,"uid":55597,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"linux?"},{"pid":"3323bafa0589c27c8da5acc06a4268c58bf1cfc0","tid":1986660,"uid":58209,"like":4,